{"tid":1693393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝被周到跳閘","createTime":"2019-11-04T14:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T15:53:38.000Z","uid":319430,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"02c558eb6cf81e6f460c1425e20d21d3e996829a","tid":1693393,"uid":319430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:37:19.000Z","msg":"今朝如常跳閘,因為平時跳開果個閘都知安全 加上環顧左四周覺得係穩陣 跳完之後冇急步跑走 點知俾個便衣職員捉住,本身仲諗住同佢理論(我認我on9左)。<br />\n<br />\n說時遲那時快,已經有個良好市民幫手捉埋我一份。但其實我身邊有好多戴曬口罩既手足,人數上其實多好多,我唔係叫你地私了佢地,佢地都係履行緊職責。不過你地可以嘗試一下救人,如果對方人數唔多的話,eg推開佢,淨係出把口幫唔到件事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴口罩唔淨係政治表態,仲方便行動阿各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f621e9160e1d86b895baf951c3ee418927700001","tid":1693393,"uid":216888,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:38:23.000Z","msg":"都講餵食野 屌 仲跳"},{"pid":"369d9f8b4cf45691322ca22a0be114a865bbe531","tid":1693393,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"留意到附近有人挨住就唔好太淡定 跳完即跑"},{"pid":"7c26ffcb24a6e23cb4546854c0418024a62166cd","tid":1693393,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"想保住份工而又有罷工效果？輪更制幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樽頸？攬炒？不如試下輪更啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0f662a6d42f499be23cb52bf269f4031192b8b5e","tid":1693393,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"個以為自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc0c8b2ef033dc6b48de10a0314b98b6550cd76","tid":1693393,"uid":216556,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f621e9160e1d86b895baf951c3ee418927700001","tid":1693393,"uid":216888,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:38: